>> STARTING AT WORLD WAR I,

00:24.824 --> 00:26.793 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
EVERY BOMB, EVERY BULLET, EVERY

00:26.793 --> 00:28.828 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WEAPON THAT WE HAVE DEVELOPED

00:28.828 --> 00:31.131 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
FOR DEFENSE PURPOSES HAS BEEN

00:31.131 --> 00:32.332 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DEVELOPED, DESIGNED,

00:32.332 --> 00:33.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MANUFACTURED, THROUGH INDUSTRIAL

00:33.566 --> 00:36.036 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
PROCESSES, THEN TESTED, AND

00:36.036 --> 00:37.170 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
EVENTUALLY IN MANY CASES

00:37.170 --> 00:38.938 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DISPOSED OF AS THEY GET OLD

00:38.938 --> 00:40.140 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
