01:47.307 --> 01:48.475 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
>> SO, WE OBTAINED A LIST THAT

01:48.475 --> 01:50.376 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HAD BEEN COMPILED INTERNALLY

01:50.376 --> 01:52.178 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WITHIN THE E.P.A., AND IT LISTED

01:52.178 --> 01:53.947 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
