02:06.793 --> 02:09.929 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CONTRACTORS, AS OPPOSED TO NASA,

02:09.929 --> 02:10.964 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
AND A COUPLE OF OTHER PRIVATE

02:10.964 --> 02:12.899 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
COMPANIES.

02:12.899 --> 02:14.667 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
THOSE SITES STILL TODAY BURN

02:14.667 --> 02:16.202 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ANYWHERE FROM A COUPLE HUNDRED

02:16.202 --> 02:18.037 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
THOUSAND POUNDS OF EXPLOSIVES A

02:18.037 --> 02:19.873 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
YEAR, UP TO 15 MILLION POUNDS OF

02:19.873 --> 02:21.040 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
EXPLOSIVES A YEAR.

02:21.040 --> 02:21.975 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
>> Sreenivasan: SO ONE OF THE

02:21.975 --> 02:22.909 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
PLACES THAT YOU PROFILED

02:22.909 --> 02:23.877 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ACTUALLY HAD AN ELEMENTARY

02:23.877 --> 02:25.345 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
SCHOOL NOT TOO FAR AWAY, THERE

