02:34.888 --> 02:36.189 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WHAT WE KNOW IS THAT IN THE

02:36.189 --> 02:37.524 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
PLACE THAT I LOOKED AT, RADFORD,

02:37.524 --> 02:39.692 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
VIRGINIA; COLFAX, LOUISIANA IS

02:39.692 --> 02:40.760 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ANOTHER TOWN; AND IN OTHER

