03:00.547 --> 03:01.714 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
BUT PART OF WHAT WE FOCUSED ON

03:01.714 --> 03:03.249 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
IN THIS STORY THIS WEEK IS THE

